  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 117–Tommy's Breakfast.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第117课——汤米的早餐。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "What does she mean by change in the last sentence?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她在最后一句话中说的change是什么意思？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "When my husband was going into the dining room this morning, he dropped some coins on the floor.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "今天早上我丈夫走进餐厅时，把一些硬币掉在了地板上。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "There were coins everywhere.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "到处都是硬币。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "We looked for them, but we could not find them all.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们找了找，但没能把它们全找到。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "While we were having breakfast, our little boy, Tommy, found two small coins on the floor.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们吃早饭时，小儿子汤米在地板上找到了两枚小硬币。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "He put them both into his mouth.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他把两枚硬币都放进了嘴里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "We both tried to get the coins, but it was too late.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们俩都想把硬币拿出来，但已经太晚了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "Tommy had already swallowed them.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "汤米已经把它们咽下去了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "Later that morning, when I was doing the housework, my husband phoned me from the office.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那天上午晚些时候，我正在做家务，丈夫从办公室打来电话。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "How's Tommy?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“汤米怎么样了？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "he asked.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他问。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "I don't know, I answered.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我不知道，”我回答，"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "Tommy's been to the toilet three times this morning, but I haven't had any change yet.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“汤米今天上午上了三次厕所，但我还没看到什么零钱。”"
      }
    }
  ],
